{"tid":1642770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"粗略用Facebook messenger 搵一個人(或者上網工具）位置嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-10T00:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T19:02:22.000Z","uid":322524,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"916200b69880b4d54f5baa8c7cd88dd7daedf33d","tid":1642770,"uid":322524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">粗略用Facebook messenger 搵一個人(或者上網工具）位置嘅方法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 你要知嗰個人嘅Facebook Account，可以同佢用Facebook messenger聯絡到<br />\n<br />\n2. 瀏覽器只開一個版頁(其他分頁，所有會上網連線嘅程式, 包括係背後運行緊嘅apps，甚至藍牙，暫時關閉，否則會有好多其他嘅IP address 顯示）<br />\n<br />\n3. 同嗰個你有懷疑嘅人facebook 開始傾計，佢唔識你，唔啋你，唔理你都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n4. 開 command prompt <br />\n- Windows: Start &gt; Run &gt; cmd. <br />\n- Mac: Applications&gt; Utility &gt; Terminal <br />\n- 輸入 netstat -an<br />\n- 一大堆現有嘅連結會出咗嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXd7dQM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXd7dQM.png&h=cb637703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲IP address 有Facebook 嘅，亦有Apple 嘅。只有一組係有古怪<br />\n<br />\n5. 去 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><a href=\"https://www.ip-adress.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ip-adress.com%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX55B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=d9b76fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ip-adress.com/</a></span> , 輸入每個有可疑嘅IP，會顯示到嗰個ip address 所在經緯度....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFMMupq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFMMupq.png&h=68aed169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 用google map 或者其他地圖去將嗰D經緯度職,轉換番地理位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbcG2KW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbcG2KW.png&h=29c6671b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNote <br />\n1. 呢個方法主要係以 IP address 去搵果部上緊網嘅電腦/手機/平板好粗略嘅位置<br />\n2. 如果有更準確嘅方法歡迎分享, 集思廣益<br />\n3. 只係搵到對方用緊嘅上網上工具，或者佢最近嘅Server，嘅位置。但唔會證明到傾緊計嗰個係咪account 本人還是俾人盜用緊<br />\n4. 用vpn 應該會唔準確<br />\n5. 只要有IP address 都已經好有用<br />\n6. 自己Facebook account有冇會引致麻煩嘅嘢，清好先"},{"pid":"b66e5abee79062f08993f9ae3437d89bce285c6a","tid":1642770,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"59506068639d7bb8917bd7005747296872c71a84","tid":1642770,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"點為之有古怪的up address?"},{"pid":"21d0559e5b6f2e3eb914c22c274beb72cd5a4cff","tid":1642770,"uid":329453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"好詳細, 回塘IT佬表示 正!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我諗好多人都未必明"},{"pid":"196f83990b4efee6deb6e1319de20e3141e24eea","tid":1642770,"uid":226337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916200b69880b4d54f5baa8c7cd88dd7daedf33d","tid":1642770,"uid":322524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">粗略用Facebook messenger 搵一個人(或者上網工具）位置嘅方法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 你要知嗰個人嘅Facebook Account，可以同佢用Facebook messenger聯絡到<br />\n<br />\n2. 瀏覽器只開一個版頁(其他分頁，所有會上網連線嘅程式, 包括係背後運行緊嘅apps，甚至藍牙，暫時關閉，否則會有好多其他嘅IP address 顯示）<br />\n<br />\n3. 同嗰個你有懷疑嘅人facebook 開始傾計，佢唔識你，唔啋你，唔理你都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n4. 開 command prompt <br />\n- Windows: Start &gt; Run &gt; cmd. <br />\n- Mac: Applications&gt; Utility &gt; Terminal <br />\n- 輸入 netstat -an<br />\n- 一大堆現有嘅連結會出咗嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXd7dQM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXd7dQM.png&h=cb637703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲IP address 有Facebook 嘅，亦有Apple 嘅。只有一組係有古怪<br />\n<br />\n5. 去 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><a href=\"https://www.ip-adress.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ip-adress.com%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX55B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=d9b76f